eldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.ofList\">FieldStatistic.ofList</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.crAnStatistics\">crAnStatistics</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.take\">List.take</a> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span>)</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a>     <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/ExchangeSign.html#FieldStatistic.exchangeSign\">FieldStatistic.exchangeSign</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.crAnStatistics\">crAnStatistics</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.get\">get</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span>)</span>)</span>\n      <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.ofList\">FieldStatistic.ofList</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.crAnStatistics\">crAnStatistics</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.take\">List.take</a> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/NormalOrder.html#FieldSpecification.normalOrderEquiv\">normalOrderEquiv</a> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/NormalOrder.html#FieldSpecification.normalOrderList\">normalOrderList</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span>)</span>)</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, a list `φs = φ₀…φₙ` of `𝓕.CrAnFieldOp` and an `i < φs.length`,\nthen\n`normalOrderSign (φ₀…φᵢ₋₁φᵢ₊₁…φₙ)` is equal to the product of\n- `normalOrderSign φ₀…φₙ`,\n- `𝓢(φᵢ, φ₀…φᵢ₋₁)` i.e. the sign needed to remove `φᵢ` from `φ₀…φₙ`,\n- `𝓢(φᵢ, _)` where `_` is the list of elements appearing before `φᵢ` after normal ordering,\n  i.e.\n  the sign needed to insert `φᵢ` back into the normal-ordered list at the correct place. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/NormalOrder.html#FieldSpecification.normalOrderSign_eraseIdx","kind":"theorem","line":347,"name":"FieldSpecification.normalOrderSign_eraseIdx","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L347-L360"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/NormalOrder.html#FieldSpecification.normalOrderList_eraseIdx_normalOrderEquiv\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">normalOrderList_eraseIdx_normalOrderEquiv</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Fin\">Fin</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"