=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/NormalOrder.html#FieldSpecification.instIsTransCrAnFieldOpNormalOrderRel\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">instIsTransCrAnFieldOpNormalOrderRel</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Defs/Unbundled.html#IsTrans\">IsTrans</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span> <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/NormalOrder.html#FieldSpecification.normalOrderRel\">normalOrderRel</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Normal ordering is transitive. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/NormalOrder.html#FieldSpecification.instIsTransCrAnFieldOpNormalOrderRel","kind":"instance","line":32,"name":"FieldSpecification.instIsTransCrAnFieldOpNormalOrderRel","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L32-L34"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/NormalOrder.html#FieldSpecification.instIsTotalCrAnFieldOpNormalOrderRel\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">instIsTotalCrAnFieldOpNormalOrderRel</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div clas